        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Stud earrings are among the most timeless and versatile pieces in any jewelry collection. Whether worn as part of your daily look or reserved for special occasions, their simple elegance can instantly elevate your style. But behind every perfect pair lies a thoughtful choice - of carat size, setting, and design. In this guide, we’ll explore the essentials of choosing the right studs for you, including carat size guidance, setting types and tips for selecting styles suited for everyday wear and special occasions.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3mEYbJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding Carat Size: A Guide to Choosing the Right Sparkle",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding Carat Size: A Guide to Choosing the Right Sparkle</h2><p>Carat size is one of the first and most important factors to consider when selecting stud earrings. It affects not only the appearance but also how comfortable and practical the studs are for your lifestyle</p>",
            "custom_id": "understanding",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Lk3hpe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Everyday Carat Size",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Everyday Carat Size</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_C4KUKT": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Everyday_Carat_Size.png",
            "text": "<p>For everyday wear, subtlety and comfort are key. Studs between 0.25 to 0.75 carats per ear offer a balanced sparkle that complements both casual and professional outfits. These smaller sizes are lightweight, easy to wear all day, and elegant enough for understated sophistication.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "cut",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1ct-half-eternity-emerald-diamond-band",
              "portuguese-entwine-bypass-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_A8fUE6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Occasion Carat Size",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Occasion Carat Size</h3>",
            "custom_id": "occasion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ry4cQt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Occassion_Crat_Size.png",
            "text": "<p>If you’re choosing studs for special occasions, larger stones such as 1 carat or more per ear create a striking presence and deliver noticeable brilliance. They pair beautifully with formal attire, adding glamour without overwhelming your overall look.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "marquise-bezel-diamond-stud-earrings",
              "0-50-ct-pear-solitaire-cascade-hoops-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cECh6h": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When exploring your options, you can refer to the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a> to understand how carat size influences price and appearance. Lucira’s lab-grown diamonds offer the same dazzling beauty as natural ones at an exceptional value and with sustainable craftsmanship.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Setting Types: Prong, Bezel, and Halo Explained",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Setting Types: Prong, Bezel, and Halo Explained</h2><p>The setting of your diamond studs not only secures the stone but also defines the overall aesthetic. Each type offers a unique balance between style, security, and shine.</p>",
            "custom_id": "setting",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jXMxqw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Prong Setting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Prong Setting</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XgNzg9": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Prong_Setting.png",
            "text": "<p>The prong setting is a timeless classic. Small metal prongs hold the diamond securely while allowing maximum light exposure, resulting in exceptional brilliance. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1-66ct-round-diamond-prong-stackable-ring",
              "0-59ct-three-stone-diamond-prong-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rwbCHF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This setting works beautifully for both small and large stones, making it a popular choice for those who love sparkle and tradition</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Bezel Setting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Bezel Setting</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_BiE3eV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bezel_Setting.png",
            "text": "<p>For a more modern and practical choice, the bezel setting encircles the diamond completely in metal. This design offers superior protection against knocks and snags, making it ideal for everyday wear. It’s sleek, secure, and perfect for people with an active lifestyle or minimalist aesthetic.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-22ct-half-eternity-bezel-diamond-band",
              "bezel-set-pear-solitaire-stud-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Halo Setting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Halo Setting</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_CfQrW8": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Halo_Setting.png",
            "text": "<p>The halo setting features a central diamond surrounded by a circle of smaller stones, amplifying the overall brilliance and making the center stone appear larger. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_P7RTNg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This glamorous setting is perfect for those seeking extra sparkle for special occasions. It’s bold yet timeless - ideal when you want to make a statement.</p><p>To explore these designs further, browse Lucira’s diverse<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">collections</span></a>, where each setting is crafted with precision and artistry to suit various tastes and occasions.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xaXyJh": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choosing Studs for Daily Wear vs. Occasion Wear",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Choosing Studs for Daily Wear vs. Occasion Wear</h2><p>Different settings and carat sizes serve different purposes. Here’s how to choose wisely depending on how and when you’ll wear your studs.</p>",
            "custom_id": "choosing",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qqnrpi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Studs for Everyday Wear",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Studs for Everyday Wear</h3><p>For daily wear, choose designs that combine elegance with practicality. Bezel or four-prong settings are idea - they’re comfortable, durable, and secure. Opt for smaller carat sizes (0.25–0.75 per ear) and neutral metal tones like white gold or platinum for a clean, polished look that pairs well with everything from office attire to casual outfits.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_pgr7g4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Studs for Special Occasions",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Studs for Special Occasions</h3><p>For occasion wear, this is your chance to indulge in extra sparkle and size. Consider halo or multi-prong settings for added brilliance and visual impact. Larger carats (1 or more per ear) can beautifully complement evening gowns or festive ensembles. Pairing your studs with a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> enhances the look with warmth and sophistication.</p><p>Those who prefer an eco-conscious sparkle can complete their look with a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond necklace</span></a>, reflecting Lucira’s commitment to sustainability and elegance.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Expert Tips for Choosing the Perfect Stud Earrings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Expert Tips for Choosing the Perfect Stud Earrings</h2><p>Finding your ideal pair of studs involves more than just picking a carat size or setting. Here are some essential tips to guide your decision:</p>",
            "custom_id": "expert",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_QCVqBz": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Experts_Tips_for_Choosing_The_Perfect_Stud_Earring_jpg.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mFyxhe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h4>1. Match the Stud Size to Your Face Shape</h4><p>Smaller studs suit delicate features, while larger carats balance broader or rounder faces beautifully. Try different sizes to see which proportions flatter you best.</p><h4>2. Consider Your Daily Routine</h4><p>If you wear your studs every day, choose secure settings like bezel or four-prong designs. Avoid large stones that may catch on clothing or hair.</p><h4>3. Choose the Right Metal for Your Skin Tone</h4><p>White gold and platinum complement cool skin tones, while yellow and rose gold enhance warmer undertones. Matching the metal to your complexion adds harmony to your overall look.</p><h4>4. Think About Pairing Options</h4><p>Studs are incredibly versatile - pair them with a dainty chain or a statement necklace for different moods. Lucira’s collections offer a range of designs that mix and match effortlessly.</p><h4>5. Invest in Quality and Comfort</h4><p>Look for secure backings and precise craftsmanship. High-quality studs, like those found at Lucira, ensure both lasting comfort and enduring shine.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_DCGjk9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Where to Find Your Perfect Studs",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Where to Find Your Perfect Studs</h2><p>Lucira offers a refined selection of diamond studs designed to suit every personality and occasion. Whether you prefer a delicate everyday pair or a bold showstopper, Lucira’s craftsmanship ensures brilliance in every detail. Visit the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur Lucira Store</span></a> to explore their stunning collection in person, or browse online for elegant designs that reflect your style and story.</p>",
            "custom_id": "where",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_QFAMzA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Thoughts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Thoughts</h2><p>Stud earrings are the cornerstone of any jewelry collection - versatile, elegant, and endlessly wearable. By understanding carat size, setting types, and how to match styles to your lifestyle, you can find a pair that complements both your everyday moments and your most special occasions. Explore <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira’s</span></a> fine selection and discover how a single pair of studs can redefine simplicity with sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": "final",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
